00:02:56.120 --> 00:02:58.630
So it starts there, and
then goes on forever.

00:02:58.630 --> 00:03:00.530
And if you remember,
that's what a ray is.

00:03:00.530 --> 00:03:04.026
One starting point,
but goes on forever.

00:03:04.026 --> 00:03:05.900
Or one way to think
about it, goes on forever

00:03:05.900 --> 00:03:07.480
in only one direction.

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:09.750
So that is a ray.

00:03:09.750 --> 00:03:11.609
