a starting point and an ending

00:03:14.150 --> 00:03:16.649
point, or you could call this
the start point and the ending

00:03:16.649 --> 00:03:19.260
point, but it doesn't go on
forever in either direction.

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:23.690
So this right over
